description: Recipe Finder can help you find a good recipe based on what you have in your fridge. You can provide a list of ingredients you have as well as provide a type of dish that you are trying to make. You can quickly bounce ideas off recipe finder with the ingredients you have so you never end up wasting any food!
exampleInteractions: Alexa Ask recipe finder what I can make with beef and rice
Alexa Ask recipe finder what soup I can make with chicken
name: Recipe Finder By Ingredients
shortDescription: Recipe Finder can help you find a good recipe based on what you have in your fridge.
